  <bodyText><![CDATA[<h2>Group walking holidays in Europe</h2>
<p><img src="/media/13108708/malcesine_lake_garda_walking_along_monte_baldo-1.jpg" alt="group walking" data-udi="umb://media/09f114acd38e4b259c68366ed7b7a46d" /></p>
<p>Explore breathtaking landscapes with your favourite people. Whether conquering peaks, strolling serene lakes, or uncovering hidden trails, our group walking holidays are the perfect fit. </p>
<p>With our 'Stay and Walk' holidays, you'll have a comfortable base to return to after a day of adventure. Walk at your own pace or join a local expert who’ll share their favourite trails. And with us, you can walk as much or as little as you like.</p>
<p><strong>Ideal for:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Walking groups of all abilities</li>
<li>Groups of friends</li>
<li>Outdoor lovers</li>
</ul>
<p>Your group, your adventure - let us handle the details, so you can focus on making unforgettable memories.</p>
<div style="max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-grey c-card--generic-shadow">
<h3 style="text-align: center;">Want 10% off your group walking holiday?</h3>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span>Discover our selection of holidays that have an enhanced group discount of 10% for groups of 10+</span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/e6b635ce7c8b4586a602fd435366695f" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e6b635ce7c8b4586a602fd435366695f}" title="Group Walking Holiday Offers" class="InfinityNumber c-btn">View deals</a></p>
</div>
<h2 style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 30px;">Why choose our group walking holidays</h2>
<!-- Row container with flex layout and wrap -->
<div style="display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 20px; justify-content: center;"><!-- Card 1 -->
<div style="flex: 1 1 21%; max-width: 21%; min-width: 280px; margin: 10px; padding: 20px; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0px 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);">
<h3 style="margin-top: 0; font-size: 1.2em;">Set your own pace</h3>
<p>Craft your ideal holiday experience, whether that means an early morning hike or enjoying a leisurely breakfast in bed.</p>
</div>
<!-- Card 2 -->
<div style="flex: 1 1 21%; max-width: 21%; min-width: 280px; margin: 10px; padding: 20px; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0px 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);">
<h3 style="margin-top: 0; font-size: 1.2em;">In resort reps</h3>
<p>Our knowledgeable reps provide expert advice on local walks, connect with you before departure, and support you throughout your stay.</p>
</div>
<!-- Card 3 -->
<div style="flex: 1 1 21%; max-width: 21%; min-width: 280px; margin: 10px; padding: 20px; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0px 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);">
<h3 style="margin-top: 0; font-size: 1.2em;">Exclusive discount</h3>
<p>Get 5% off when booking a group walking holiday for 10 people or more. Just speak to our reservations team directly for more details.</p>
</div>
<!-- Card 4 -->
<div style="flex: 1 1 21%; max-width: 21%; min-width: 280px; margin: 10px; padding: 20px; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0px 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);">
<h3 style="margin-top: 0; font-size: 1.2em;">Included guided walks</h3>
<p>In many of our resorts, join up to two exclusive guided day walks led by a professional guide, with easy-to-moderate and more challenging trail options. Subject to limited availability.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-grey c-card--generic-shadow">
<h3 style="text-align: center;">How to book your holiday</h3>
<p style="text-align: center;">Simply give us a call to book your holiday. Flights, hotel and transport? We’ve got you covered.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="tel:01483791111" class="InfinityNumber c-btn">Call us to book today</a></p>
</div>
<p> </p>
<h2 style="text-align: center;">Our top picks: featured resorts for group walking holidays</h2>
<p style="text-align: center;">Explore our top group walking destinations across Austria, Italy, Slovenia, and Switzerland, offering breathtaking trails and unforgettable views.</p>
<div class="row">
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow u-text-center">
<div class="c-card__img"><img src="/media/13108509/mayrhofen_penken_mountain_reservoir_adobestock_384417196.jpg" alt="mayrhofen holidays" data-udi="umb://media/75c686bebda64662aeec4283672d648d" /></div>
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/594483304a5f4b47844b444df2c9d975" href="/{localLink:umb://document/594483304a5f4b47844b444df2c9d975}" title="Mayrhofen">Mayrhofen, Austria </a></h3>
<p>Discover trails starting right in town, lifts to scenic heights, and themed walks with mountain hut feasts. Get the Zillertal Activcard for added adventure</p>
<div class="c-card__cta-list c-card__cta-list--stacked"><a data-udi="umb://document/594483304a5f4b47844b444df2c9d975" href="/{localLink:umb://document/594483304a5f4b47844b444df2c9d975}" title="Mayrhofen" class="c-btn c-btn--secondary c-btn--mid c-btn--wide u-text-center">Mayrhofen Holidays</a></div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow u-text-center">
<div class="c-card__img"><img src="/media/13108510/obergurgl_oetztal_adobestock_24373790.jpg" alt="obergurgl walking holidays" data-udi="umb://media/af9d693194914d4da670c309a127d753" /></div>
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/5b2012f465d44823b6f9ba4c3b40fd4b" href="/{localLink:umb://document/5b2012f465d44823b6f9ba4c3b40fd4b}" title="Obergurgl">Obergurgl, Austria</a></h3>
<p>Walk the Diamond of the Alps. Explore hundreds of kilometres of high-altitude trails, soak in breathtaking views from the Hohe Mut ridge, and indulge in Tyrolean cuisine and luxurious spas.</p>
<div class="c-card__cta-list c-card__cta-list--stacked"><a data-udi="umb://document/5b2012f465d44823b6f9ba4c3b40fd4b" href="/{localLink:umb://document/5b2012f465d44823b6f9ba4c3b40fd4b}" title="Obergurgl" class="c-btn c-btn--secondary c-btn--mid c-btn--wide u-text-center">Obergurgl Holidays</a></div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow u-text-center">
<div class="c-card__img"><img src="/media/13108706/adobestock_170951228.jpg" alt="cha,monix walking holidays" data-udi="umb://media/f0dbf00a4bd14734bb31f5f7faf8fe80" /></div>
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/2735e2389f7c411cb3061226ce7548d1" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2735e2389f7c411cb3061226ce7548d1}" title="Chamonix">Chamonix, France</a></h3>
<p>Chamonix offers breathtaking trails for all, from gentle valley walks to alpine trails on the Tour du Mont Blanc. With panoramic views, lifts, and the charm of a bustling town, it’s the perfect base for group walking holidays.</p>
<div class="c-card__cta-list c-card__cta-list--stacked"><a data-udi="umb://document/2735e2389f7c411cb3061226ce7548d1" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2735e2389f7c411cb3061226ce7548d1}" title="Chamonix" class="c-btn c-btn--secondary c-btn--mid c-btn--wide u-text-center">Chamonix Holidays</a></div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow u-text-center">
<div class="c-card__img"><img src="/media/13108707/selva_val_gardena_dolomites_inghams_rep_on_the_passo_sella_sassolungo.jpg" alt="selva" data-udi="umb://media/97d0d1317f524b759bf106c01b4d4838" /></div>
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/4c9fc09241f14e3c80acb89b5c9226dd" href="/{localLink:umb://document/4c9fc09241f14e3c80acb89b5c9226dd}" title="Selva">Selva, Italy</a></h3>
<p>A Dolomites dream. Walk iconic peaks, explore endless trails, and surround yourself in vibrant local culture. Perfect for group adventures and unforgettable mountain memories</p>
<div class="c-card__cta-list c-card__cta-list--stacked"><a data-udi="umb://document/4c9fc09241f14e3c80acb89b5c9226dd" href="/{localLink:umb://document/4c9fc09241f14e3c80acb89b5c9226dd}" title="Selva" class="c-btn c-btn--secondary c-btn--mid c-btn--wide u-text-center">Selva Holidays</a></div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow u-text-center">
<div class="c-card__img"><img src="/media/13108643/kranjska_gora_steinbock_statue_at_lake_jasna-1.jpg" alt="kranjska gora holidays" data-udi="umb://media/8fa69c6e2ca34f8186c72cc991d1239d" /></div>
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/9b6cf6eac79541f5850e141e41a071ab" href="/{localLink:umb://document/9b6cf6eac79541f5850e141e41a071ab}" title="Kranjska Gora">Kranjska Gora, Slovenia</a></h3>
<p>Walk Slovenia's stunning Julian Alps! Discover picturesque villages, turquoise lakes, and thrilling outdoor activities. Unwind in this alpine paradise, perfect for nature lovers and adventure seekers alike.</p>
<div class="c-card__cta-list c-card__cta-list--stacked"><a data-udi="umb://document/9b6cf6eac79541f5850e141e41a071ab" href="/{localLink:umb://document/9b6cf6eac79541f5850e141e41a071ab}" title="Kranjska Gora" class="c-btn c-btn--secondary c-btn--mid c-btn--wide u-text-center">Kranjska Gora Holidays</a></div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow u-text-center">
<div class="c-card__img"><img src="/media/13108642/interlaken_thun_city_view-1.jpg" alt="selva" data-udi="umb://media/863fee7d89f841709f03cccf7a615e54" /></div>
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/7456bae57241449a84a68959b62b2aba" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7456bae57241449a84a68959b62b2aba}" title="Interlaken">Interlaken, Switzerland</a></h3>
<p>This is your summer adventure playground. Walk mountains, paraglide, cruise at sunset - all surrounded by stunning lakes and cosy cafes. The perfect mix of thrills and chills.</p>
<div class="c-card__cta-list c-card__cta-list--stacked"><a data-udi="umb://document/7456bae57241449a84a68959b62b2aba" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7456bae57241449a84a68959b62b2aba}" title="Interlaken" class="c-btn c-btn--secondary c-btn--mid c-btn--wide u-text-center">Interlaken Holidays</a></div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<p> </p>
<h2 style="text-align: center;">Our favourite hotels for group walking holidays</h2>
<p> </p>
<div class="row">
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow u-text-center">
<div class="c-card__img"><img src="/media/13108592/inghams_italy_dolomites_selva_hotel_mignon_exterior.jpg" alt="hotel mignon" data-udi="umb://media/361c99ce4f2d4ffca5c9266a9ca595e3" /></div>
<h4>Hotel Mignon, Selva</h4>
<div class="c-card__content">
<p>Ideal for group holidays, Hotel Mignon in Selva’s car-free centre offers easy access to mountain trails, 31 spacious rooms, local cuisine, and scenic balcony views for a charming alpine experience.</p>
</div>
<div class="c-card__cta-list"><a data-udi="umb://document/e8557eec82d947e89e7aa9047035cce1" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e8557eec82d947e89e7aa9047035cce1}" title="Hotel Mignon" class="c-btn c-btn--secondary c-btn--mid c-btn--wide u-text-center">View Hotel</a></div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow u-text-center">
<div class="c-card__img"><img src="/media/13109605/hotel_die_sonne_saalbach_zirmstube_lounge.jpg" alt="hotel sonne" data-udi="umb://media/7d9e3b0df2394a9493198a65aa4db361" /></div>
<h4>Hotel Sonne, Saalbach</h4>
<div class="c-card__content">
<p>The all-inclusive Hotel Sonne, located between Saalbach and Hinterglemm, offers easy access to walking lifts and village amenities. Enjoy excellent spa facilities, supervised kids' activities, rustic Austrian décor, and a variety of food and drinks throughout the day.</p>
</div>
<div class="c-card__cta-list"><a data-udi="umb://document/caf494c6b3d9432b9a74641cd2823782" href="/{localLink:umb://document/caf494c6b3d9432b9a74641cd2823782}" title="Hotel Sonne (Saalbach)" class="c-btn c-btn--secondary c-btn--mid c-btn--wide u-text-center">View Hotel</a></div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow u-text-center">
<div class="c-card__img"><img src="/media/13109596/revier_mountain_lodge_saas_fee_exterior.jpg" alt="mountain lodge" data-udi="umb://media/1eb4f653304b4ce4b180223bda99e589" /></div>
<h4>Revier Mountain Lodge</h4>
<p>The Revier Mountain Lodge combines sustainability with quality, holding a certified Green Key label. Its panoramic cabins blend traditional wooden touches with modern design, offering comfort, natural light, and stunning mountain views.</p>
<div class="c-card__content"><a data-udi="umb://document/151ce5cdabf84259b16352fb7aeca636" href="/{localLink:umb://document/151ce5cdabf84259b16352fb7aeca636}" title="Revier Mountain Lodge" class="c-btn c-btn--secondary c-btn--mid c-btn--wide u-text-center">View Hotel</a></div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-grey c-card--generic-shadow">
<h3 style="text-align: center;">How to book your holiday</h3>
<p style="text-align: center;">Simply give us a call to book your holiday. Flights, hotel and transport? We’ve got you covered.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="tel:01483791111" class="InfinityNumber c-btn">Call us to book today</a></p>
</div>]]></bodyText>
